%% Diagram: Stale write corrupts data when there is no fencing
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C1 as Client 1
    participant L as Lock Service
    participant S as Storage
    participant C2 as Client 2

    C1->>L: Acquire(resource)
    L-->>C1: Granted (30 s lease)
    Note over C1: GC pause begins (45 s)
    Note over L: Lease expires at 30 s
    Note over C1: ...still paused...

    C2->>L: Acquire(resource)
    L-->>C2: Granted

    C2->>S: Write "value-B"
    S-->>C2: OK

    Note over C1: GC pause ends
    C1->>S: Write "value-A" (stale!)
    S-->>C1: OK (no fencing)
    Note over S: Last write wins → corruption
